ZH: 我们预定了房间，准备明天入住。
EN: We have booked the room and are ready to check in tomorrow.

ZH: 入住时，请出示您的身份证件。
EN: Please present your identification when checking in.

ZH: 入住前请完成登记手续。
EN: Please complete the registration process before check-in.

ZH: 酒店要求入住时支付一部分押金。
EN: The hotel requires a partial deposit upon check-in.

ZH: 入住的客人可以享受免费早餐。
EN: Guests who check in can enjoy a complimentary breakfast.

ZH: 如果您有特殊需求，请提前告知入住人员。
EN: If you have any special requests, please inform the check-in staff in advance.

ZH: 入住人数超过规定的最大容纳人数会收取额外费用。
EN: Additional charges will apply if the number of occupants exceeds the maximum allowed for check-in.

ZH: 已经预订的房间只保留到晚上六点，请尽早入住。
EN: The reserved room will only be held until 6 pm, so please check in early.

ZH: 入住前，请确认您的预订信息是否准确无误。
EN: Before check-in, please verify that your reservation information is correct.

ZH: 入住时请带上您的确认单和有效的信用卡。
EN: Please bring your confirmation receipt and a valid credit card when checking in.

ZH: 入住期间，请遵守酒店的房间规定和行为准则。
EN: Please adhere to the hotel's room regulations and code of conduct during your stay.

ZH: 客房清洁人员将在您入住后的每天向您打扫房间。
EN: The housekeeping staff will clean your room every day after check-in.

ZH: 如果需要延迟退房，请在入住当天向前台提出申请。
EN: If you require a late check-out, please request it at the front desk on the day of check-in.

ZH: 入住时，酒店会收取一定的服务费用。
EN: The hotel charges a service fee upon check-in.

ZH: 入住时，客人可以选择是否参加酒店的旅游观光活动。
EN: Guests can choose whether or not to participate in the hotel's sightseeing activities upon check-in.

ZH: 入住期间，如果有任何问题或需求，请随时联系前台。
EN: If you have any questions or needs during your stay, please contact the front desk at any time.

ZH: 入住期间，请保管好您的贵重物品和重要文件。
EN: Please keep your valuable belongings and important documents secure during your stay.

ZH: 入住时，客人需要签署一份住宿协议。
EN: Guests are required to sign an accommodation agreement upon check-in.

ZH: 入住期间，请遵守酒店的安全规定和消防措施。
EN: Please comply with the hotel's safety regulations and fire prevention measures during your stay.

ZH: 入住后，如需修改预订信息，请与前台工作人员联系。
EN: If you need to modify your reservation information after check-in, please contact the front desk staff.
